## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of data up to October 2023 and may not reflect the most current developments in the pandemic's impact. Additionally, the findings are based on surveys and reports that may have inherent biases or limitations in scope. Further research is needed to capture the ongoing and evolving effects of COVID-19 on global populations.